{"tid":386943,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦又開唔到機","createTime":"2017-09-04T09:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:57:37.000Z","uid":83189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"545504ba87e98d43d83060b7f775cd1d81cf8df1","tid":386943,"uid":83189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"詳細情況<br />\n<br />\n部腦一時開到一時開唔到<br />\n有幾次試過關機既時候<br />\n個mon 係無訊號 但係主機仲著緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等左好耐都係咁<br />\n<br />\n開唔到機既情況就係 個cpu個風扇轉得特別大聲 <br />\n電腦既燈都有著<br />\nGpu既燈都有著<br />\n但係個mon又係無訊號 （橙燈）<br />\n<br />\n嘗試過用擦膠擦過ram同整實條ram都係開唔到<br />\n<br />\n但係有時我唔掂佢幾個鐘再開佢就冇啦啦又可以用得番<br />\n想問應該點做<br />\n係唔係比人落左降頭...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一個鐘前用完熄左部腦 依加又開唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4dd542121d179188daca44d05addb67fed93f9","tid":386943,"uid":83189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"唔記得講 我部腦冇個蜂嗚器<br />\n所以就唔太知個狀況.."},{"pid":"80881e1bad6d941920342f79d63f922433e4bf72","tid":386943,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"BIOS POST CHECK GPU FAILED / ERROR"},{"pid":"160876ab9bd3ac732f805d16371f65007ba1bd3e","tid":386943,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"我部電腦啱啱個開機制係咁眨橙燈, 究竟邊忽壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9403d9b5190042374129893909097a1e74c2295d","tid":386943,"uid":53857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:36:06.000Z","msg":"買張debug卡或者插返個bibi<br />\n如果唔係就用排除法test下邊part野出問題"},{"pid":"099e68793f245a01a57a4c264af10f7ca4e3fe7e","tid":386943,"uid":83189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BIOS POST CHECK GPU FAILED / ERROR</blockquote><br />\n想問姐係點樣 我電腦開唔